---
---
<section class="hero" id="home">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-label">WEB DIRECTOR</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        地域とつなぐ、<br />世界とつなぐ。
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">売上にコミットするWEBディレクター</p>
      <p class="hero-desc">
        上場企業の現役社員として国際的なM&amp;A案件に携わりながら、<br class="pc-br" />
        地域の中小企業のデジタル支援を複業で行っています。
      </p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">まずは相談する</a>
        <a href="#works" class="btn-secondary">実績を見る</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-num">6<span class="stat-plus">+</span></span>
        <span class="stat-label">支援実績</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-divider"></div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-num">3</span>
        <span class="stat-label">コアサービス</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-divider"></div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-num">10<span class="stat-plus">+</span></span>
        <span class="stat-label">対応ツール</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.hero {
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding-top: 64px;
  background: var(--bg);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.hero::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: -15%;
  right: -8%;
  width: 560px;
  height: 560px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--accent-light) 0%, transparent 70%);
  pointer-events: none;
}

.hero-content {
  max-width: 720px;
  padding: 80px 0 40px;
}

.hero-label {
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.hero-title {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 6vw, 4.75rem);
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 1.2;
  color: var(--text);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.hero-sub {
  font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.8vw, 1.2rem);
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.hero-desc {
  font-size: 0.9375rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.9;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}

.pc-br {
  display: none;
}

@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .pc-br {
    display: block;
  }
}

.hero-cta {
  display: flex;
  gap: 16px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.btn-primary {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  background: var(--accent);
  color: var(--white);
  padding: 14px 32px;
  border-radius: 32px;
  font-size: 0.9375rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  transition: var(--transition);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(45, 106, 79, 0.3);
}

.btn-primary:hover {
  background: var(--accent-hover);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(45, 106, 79, 0.4);
}

.btn-secondary {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--text);
  padding: 14px 32px;
  border-radius: 32px;
  font-size: 0.9375rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
  transition: var(--transition);
}

.btn-secondary:hover {
  border-color: var(--accent);
  color: var(--accent);
}

.hero-stats {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 40px;
  padding: 32px 0 56px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
}

.stat {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 4px;
}

.stat-num {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: 2rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1;
}

.stat-plus {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  color: var(--accent);
}

.stat-label {
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

.stat-divider {
  width: 1px;
  height: 40px;
  background: var(--border);
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .hero-content {
    padding: 48px 0 32px;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    gap: 24px;
  }
}
</style>
